{"tid":1799431,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[ 行動POST ]  12.27~28  上水和你SHOP 麻煩幫手推推置頂","createTime":"2019-12-27T03:14:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-28T06:29:31.000Z","uid":329059,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"8c618b197bb4bee29724b870f43871bb28da4a5e","tid":1799431,"uid":329059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T03:14:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V4nnPOC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV4nnPOC.jpg&h=915b3ef2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/piTFBtD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpiTFBtD.jpg&h=ade0eca7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/619Yn8D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F619Yn8D.jpg&h=a126fa5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢幾日辛苦曬大家 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今日大家喺屋企休息回復體力準備27 28星期六日去上水同班水貨客再戰 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我哋要講趕走班水貨狗同埋令商場藥房關門大吉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">12月28~29日上水和你SHOP行動地點 :</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">1. 上水廣場<br />\n2. 新都廣場<br />\n3. 上水匯<br />\n4. 上水中心<br />\n5. 彩園商場<br />\n6. 街邊藥房(舊墟)</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">12月28~29日上水和你SHOP終極目標 :</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">1. 趕走水貨<br />\n2. 商場藥房落閘</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n為避免重犯前幾日既錯誤<br />\n希望大家記住目標達成就立即撤離!<br />\n快閃<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n盡量避免身穿blackbloc成為目標<br />\n但都可以帶件外套以防不時之須<br />\n<br />\n注意事項：<br />\n<br />\n1. <span style=\"color: red;\">只要唔物理攻擊便衣，便衣就耐我地唔何</span><br />\n（記住現場有記者幫手睇住，反而亂捉鬼會害到手足）<br />\n<br />\n2. <span style=\"color: violet;\">必須密切關注各TG Channel嘅情報！商場或鋪頭落閘後，綠色曱甴就會隨之而來</span><br />\n（今日幾大哨頻都有提及旺角、沙田一帶已被包圍，大家務必提高警覺）<br />\n<br />\n3. <span style=\"color: gold;\">落閘後可以去其他商場增援</span><br />\n（商場一旦落閘，之後個場就無人會再去，情報傳得比你想像中快）<br />\n<br />\n4. <span style=\"color: teal;\">避免沉迷屌曱甴</span><br />\n（屌曱甴一時爽，但因屌曱甴而引發沖突嘅流血事件多不勝數，<br />\n所以間唔中屌吓等佢哋有火都發唔出嗰下就最爽）<br />\n<br />\n5. <span style=\"color: green;\">目標達成就要「散水」</span><br />\n（就算唔想去轉場，都避免留係原地太耐成為被攻擊目標，<br />\n保持流動性，和理SHOP係持之以恆嘅活動）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n27 28 班狗會例牌封路<br />\n會隨機查人,通常主要截查咩住背囊嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有最後<br />\n唔好戀戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />做完嘢就走<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d4ed8ed4ae6faf68094f7d0fe811ba87f2d4f97","tid":1799431,"uid":329059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T03:15:46.000Z","msg":"小弟第一次開行動POST <img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/upset_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b78e69788b40544fe2701acf96f1d3204234dd7","tid":1799431,"uid":129825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T03:16:49.000Z","msg":"手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a21f43d995d7d86f51938570138adebb3435ee1","tid":1799431,"uid":343320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c618b197bb4bee29724b870f43871bb28da4a5e","tid":1799431,"uid":329059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T03:14:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V4nnPOC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV4nnPOC.jpg&h=915b3ef2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/piTFBtD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpiTFBtD.jpg&h=ade0eca7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/619Yn8D.jpg\" data-thumbn